### 用户模块 — 资料 / 关注
### 先执行 auth.http 中的 login 获取 accessToken

### @name me
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### @name updateMe
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bio": "ACGN creator",
  "location": "Shanghai",
  "website": "https://example.com",
  "nickname": "Alice",
  "avatar": "https://cdn.example.com/avatar.png",
  "background_url": "https://cdn.example.com/profile-bg.jpg"
}

###

### @name getProfile
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/profile
Accept: application/json

###

### @name listUserScreenplays
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/screenplays?page=1&page_size=20
Accept: application/json

###

### @name listUserDraftScreenplays
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/screenplays?publish_status=0&page=1&page_size=20
Accept: application/json

###

### @name listUserFavorites
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/favorites?page=1&page_size=20
Accept: application/json

###

### @name listUserLikes
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/likes?page=1&page_size=20
Accept: application/json

###

### @name listFollowers
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/followers?page=1&page_size=20
Accept: application/json

###

### @name listFollowing
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/following?page=1&page_size=20
Accept: application/json

###

### @name followStatus
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/follow-status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### @name getUser
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### @name follow
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### @name unfollow
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
